data.value:
Welcome To Survive The Day
Your aim is to live through one day and make it to midnight without dieing. You start the day at 4:00 AM and will be asked to make choices throughout the day which may cause you success or failure.
The time is displayed at the bottom left of the screen so that you can keep track of your progress of how close you are to midnight.
Can you survive the day?
